This is how to check_dict_case of dict:
   Remember that n is dict's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that pair is item i in dict
      Remember that key is item 0 in pair
      Remember that m is key's length
      Remember that j is 0
      Do this m times:
         Remember that c is item j in key
         When c is at least 65, then:
            When c is at most 90, then:
               The answer is 0
            End when
         End when
         Increase j
      End do
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is 1
